{"tid":2462972,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"黃明志首由香港人填詞既「老人痴愛」出左啦","createTime":"2021-03-26T10:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T13:02:02.000Z","uid":2110,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f3aff70154cfb5967c08b4e7ef5562e834cebce9","tid":2462972,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"依首歌係經過填詞比賽後, 由香港人勝出, 最後再係台灣拍攝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2mHi15lXZOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2mHi15lXZOk&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=b07b41a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2mHi15lXZOk</a>"},{"pid":"f34592e189c6a48d5544f1510651cb8ca831da7a","tid":2462972,"uid":2110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"我倆遇見某日某麵店<br />\n細雨飄下 一瞬間 記憶空一片<br />\n連年年月月我也不清楚<br />\n每個站也有共妳待過<br />\n去到終站 待原地 汽車都熄火<br />\n由旁人引證我只得一個<br />\n誰知道 妳在何方<br />\n遲鈍的我卻擇善遺忘<br />\n人越老越怕狀況<br />\n全視線下降<br />\n想追憶只得背影<br />\n無法可觸摸<br />\n<br />\n無奈童話中角色 只得我<br />\n為何在翻看舊頁 才知錯<br />\n熒幕前哭泣放聲<br />\n只得我很清楚<br />\n錯的因 種出果 原是我<br />\n想得多<br />\n將得過且過<br />\n<br />\n認可癡心一個"},{"pid":"d5215ac2f51dc002d88d3c85ff9a333f220b66f1","tid":2462972,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"個造型成個楊過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6030c6c5a1ccac4fe962f69f5ccb4e05b1944ae7","tid":2462972,"uid":301050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:50:38.000Z","msg":"哈哈林北終於脫毛帽拍MV了! 看了這個造型真的很想打9我自己😝 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287e2a262d4547bd65ca5139ad4e292fbd8ae19f","tid":2462972,"uid":217222,"like":0,"disli